{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"black","nameNarration":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"narration":"'Tis shocking for the fair one not to know how to play;@many a time, while playing, is love commenced.@— Ovidius, The Art of Love, Vol. III.","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":100.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bg":"bg_adv_65031.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"<78 A.D.>","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"<Pompeii>"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm24_story08","nameNarration":"Amaryllis","narration":"It was the great poet Ovid's \"The Art of Love\"@that first sparked my interest in board games.","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"When I learned that Lady Cornelia@was also interested, I thought..."},{"narration":"\"Here is my chance...to get closer to her!\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"white","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833600,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Amaryllis","narration":"Lady Cornelia is the daughter of the most@prestigious family in Pompeii...@She is a graceful, gentle and@intellectual young lady!","narrationBg":"narration","narrationCoverOpacity":140.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"I've admired her for the longest time."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_65031.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Amaryllis","narration":"And then, two years ago...","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51196_historia_paxromana/memoria_1922.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"nameNarration":"Amaryllis","narration":"For the time being, could you move the pieces@as I just taught you?","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":10.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameNarration":"Cornelia","narration":"L-like...this?"},{"nameNarration":"Amaryllis","narration":"Yes, yes!@That's my Lady Cornelia, you learn so fast...!"},{"nameNarration":"Cornelia","narration":"Thank you... Amali— Amaryllis."},{"nameNarration":"Amaryllis","narration":"Let's play a few times, and when you get used to how to@move the dice, we'll increase the number of dice, shall we?"},{"nameNarration":"Cornelia","narration":"What...? More things to think about...@It sounds difficult..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_65031.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105301,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":105301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Amaryllis","textCenter":"(Back then,)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":105301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Amaryllis","textCenter":"(Lady Cornelia also had a bit of a lisp...)"},{"nameNarration":"Amaryllis","narration":"The Hellenic name \"Amaryllis,\" which appears@in the works of the famous poet Vergil,@is a little hard to pronounce.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_65031.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"That's why many people just call me \"Amalilly\",@but Lady Cornelia insists on calling me \"Amaryllis\"@in all seriousness."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":105301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Amaryllis","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"(That kind of sincerity is also wonderful...!)"},{"bgm":"stop","nameRight":"Cornelia's Voice","textRight":"Amaryllis..."},{"nameRight":"Cornelia's Voice","textRight":"Amaryllis...?"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story20","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":105301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Amaryllis","textCenter":"[chara:105301:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Huh?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":105301,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833600,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51196_historia_paxromana/51196_ancient_gameboard.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"nameRight":"Cornelia","textRight":"Your turn."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_053.exp3.json","id":105301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"*Gasp*?!"},{"chara":[{"id":105301,"lipSynch":1}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"Hwh...! Th-that's right...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105301,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Tap*...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_65031.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833600,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Cornelia","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"...What?@You're going to stack the pieces that way?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp3.json","id":105301,"motion":100,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"Hehe... Now my defense is perfect, you see!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":833600,"motion":200,"pos":2},{"id":105301,"mouthOpen":0}],"nameRight":"Cornelia","textRight":"For me, it would have hurt more to have all@this mass coming at once, though."},{"chara":[{"id":833600,"motion":1},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":105301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_053.exp3.json","id":105301,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"Whaa...?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":105301,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":0}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"You're right,"},{"chara":[{"id":105301}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"I'm missing the perfect moment to attack by@defending an unimportant area!"},{"chara":[{"id":833600,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Cornelia","textRight":"I mean, you can go again if you want."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":105301,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Amaryllis","textLeft":"No, no need for mercy!@Even though it does hurt..."},{"nameNarration":"Amaryllis","narration":"It was me who first taught her how to play Ludus,","narrationBg":"bg_adv_65031.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"but now, I don't think I can beat her anymore..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
